{"tid":1582602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Rambo教我地私了根本係替天行道","createTime":"2019-09-20T07:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T16:42:07.000Z","uid":164402,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7498fd310029e09899668ddfe8f15c0d9cc0e7fa","tid":1582602,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"怎樣的私了才受大眾接受？一是受了極大寃屈，叫天不應，叫地不聞，法例/體制內根本無法得到公義；二是對方大奸大惡的程度，是你不只要令他受受教訓，而且你根本是替天行道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《終極血戰》故事發生在美墨邊境，沒有特朗普口頭說要建的圍牆，Rambo來去自如，有趣的是他越境挑戰賣淫黑幫，墨國中黑警不是沒有執法能力，只是當淫竇擄劫新女，黑幫會讓黑警率先享用，以致Rambo不但是為了救女，還是在墨國替天行道。<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日，日日見到有人被自殺被強姦，佢地每個人既痛苦係無法想像，算數？move on？有啲有命出番黎佢地每一晚都諗緊係新屋嶺入面發生過既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點樣move on? 甚至可能下個係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以，我地一定唔可以放過政府，放過黑警，一定要繼續出黎直到清算到全部黑警同相關人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn3.movieweb.com/i/article-content/uGpRY1P44vCUaXh7hONigfTzPuLdl7/798:50/default.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn3.movieweb.com%2Fi%2Farticle-content%2FuGpRY1P44vCUaXh7hONigfTzPuLdl7%2F798%3A50%2Fdefault.jpg&h=6d869a75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92ce055e495902bbebc38b8ac01be8a597456a5c","tid":1582602,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8m9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=d6854d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"fccd80fc3bfcd4c5290b56ca0f4cba0a5ab9143d","tid":1582602,"uid":27918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"[<strong><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">加拿大撚入</span></strong></strong>] <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>第一次</ins></span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>海外</ins></span><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>大型</ins></span><span style=\"color: red;\">籌款</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(好似係)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1582473/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1582473/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b1d6fbdd8baf3026cd3d9e20a6d75da7913896de","tid":1582602,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42534963ec1db41a3e5d044a4344aca3cc1dab68","tid":1582602,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2774257b9b078f389da0a8c8272bd4fb02ee9c59","tid":1582602,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42534963ec1db41a3e5d044a4344aca3cc1dab68","tid":1582602,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d333c97814861cd5933bec9d866cf95462df8b3","tid":1582602,"uid